      "jump_link": "./wiki/letters/2001-letter.md#p4"
    },
    {
      "year": 2002,
      "quote": "在伯克希尔，我们格外珍视成本意识。",
      "source": "berkshire_zh/2002-letter-zh.md",
      "jump_link": "./wiki/letters/2002-letter.md#p27"
    },
    {
      "year": 2003,
