      "jump_link": "./wiki/letters/2003-letter.md#p15"
    },
    {
      "year": 2004,
      "quote": "我们希望美国采取能够迅速且大幅削减经常账户赤字的政策。",
      "source": "berkshire_zh/2004-letter-zh.md",
      "jump_link": "./wiki/letters/2004-letter.md#p49"
    },
    {
      "year": 2006,
      "quote": "沃尔特没上过商学院，甚至没上过大学。",
